{ By Jessica Green For Mailonline   Published:  09:39, 25 February 2020   https://www.dailymail.co.uk//femail/article-8038673/The-impressive-renovations-captured-world.html }
Incredible photographs have captured the remarkable transformations of derelict and abandoned buildings across the world. From a church converted to a skate park and a jail turned into a hotel, the renovations were first shared in an online gallery by Bored Panda.  The collection also includes an old English courtroom that has been made into a cafe, and a former theatre in Argentina which has been transformed into a mesmerising bookstore. Here, FEMAIL reveals a selection of the best renovations...   
